<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>418 - I'm a Teapot</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        .teapot-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #d63384;
            /* Pinkish color */
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .btn-home {
            background-color: #0d6efd;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="teapot-container">
        <h1>418</h1>
        <h2>I'm a Teapot</h2>
        <p>The requested entity body is short and stout.<br>Tip me over and pour me out.</p>

        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550966871-3ed3c6227753?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
            alt="A nice ceramic teapot">

        <div>
            <a href="/" class="btn-home">Return Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>